<br>
1) Agree whole-heartedly that this needed to happen.  However, think it is now time for SoE to look hard at level limit/restricting ALL gear in the game.  It just isn't fair to take away the &quot;twink&quot; buff advantage for a wizard, but allow a melee twink to keep his gear.  Agree also that it is time to rethink where focus items, and for that matter, a lot of loot drops.  I spent about 20 levels with the same gear (bazaar bought), because nothing in those levels dropped anything better.  Was really a turn-off to the game.<br>
