<br>
The reason they dont group any more is the overpowering buffs that make it possible for them to solo to 60.  My son is going through this right now after having had to recreate is accidentally deleted enchanter.  Why bother grouping when the current buff system allows you to cast and fight without any danger of dying?<br>
<br>
I'm all for the change that is upcoming.  I've been cheering it on since I first heard about it.  It's about time.  I'm sick and tired of being stuck with Skippy The Wonder Twink who started playing the game last week and stops to ask my if they should use Lure instead of draughts.  Wait a sec!  I have too much mana!  Let me load up a lure!<br>
